Template: matrix-matrixon/hostname
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: The server (host)name of the Matrix NextServer
 This is the hostname the NextServer will be reachable at via a client.
 .
 If set to "localhost", you can connect with a client locally and clients
 from other hosts and also other NextServers will not be able to reach you!

Template: matrix-matrixon/address
Type: string
Default: 127.0.0.1
Description: The listen address of the Matrix NextServer
 This is the address the NextServer will listen on. Leave it set to 127.0.0.1
 when using a reverse proxy.

Template: matrix-matrixon/port
Type: string
Default: 6167
Description: The port of the Matrix NextServer
 This port is most often just accessed by a reverse proxy.
